WEBVTT

00:00:07.875 --> 00:00:09.574 line:93%
(Episode 17)

00:01:06.964 --> 00:01:07.964 line:93%
Where's Ha Jung?

00:01:09.535 --> 00:01:10.694 line:93%
He's sleeping inside.

00:01:21.774 --> 00:01:22.845 line:93%
Hello, Director Jang.

00:01:22.944 --> 00:01:24.914 line:93%
Hello. Please take the child.

00:01:25.285 --> 00:01:26.285 line:93%
Yes, sir.

00:01:30.615 --> 00:01:31.884 line:93%
What are you doing?

00:01:36.494 --> 00:01:38.194 line:93%
I'm just asking her to keep an eye on him.

00:01:39.125 --> 00:01:41.065 line:93%
If we raise our voices,

00:01:41.595 --> 00:01:42.834 line:93%
he might be scared.

00:02:24.905 --> 00:02:26.005 line:93%
I heard...

00:02:27.414 --> 00:02:29.014 line:93%
Pil Joo brought you here,

00:02:29.745 --> 00:02:31.944 line:93%
so you can make your own decision about the press conference.

00:02:35.285 --> 00:02:36.384 line:93%
Did you make up your mind yet?

00:02:38.655 --> 00:02:39.685 line:93%
Not yet.

00:02:41.454 --> 00:02:42.954 line:93%
What are you hesitating about?

00:02:45.095 --> 00:02:46.394 line:93%
About what I will say there.

00:02:49.134 --> 00:02:51.764 line:93%
What I should tell the press to hurt...

00:02:51.764 --> 00:02:53.965 line:93%
you and Executive Jung.

00:02:58.074 --> 00:03:00.444 line:93%
I'm hesitating because I can't come up with what to say.

00:03:46.424 --> 00:03:47.854 line:93%
For the sake of Ha Jung.

00:03:56.935 --> 00:03:58.104 line:93%
Seo Won.

00:04:01.005 --> 00:04:02.775 line:93%
I let you slide for the sake of Ha Jung...

00:04:02.775 --> 00:04:04.375 line:93%
since you're his mother.

00:04:16.354 --> 00:04:17.585 line:93%
It's a one-time deal.

00:04:20.225 --> 00:04:22.124 line:93%
And you...

00:04:24.494 --> 00:04:26.424 line:93%
used it just now.

00:04:28.994 --> 00:04:30.135 line:93%
Boo Cheon.

00:04:42.475 --> 00:04:43.544 line:93%
Now,

00:04:44.044 --> 00:04:45.184 line:93%
there is...

00:04:45.814 --> 00:04:46.845 line:93%
a reason...

00:04:49.614 --> 00:04:52.385 line:93%
I must be the chairman even if it costs my life.

00:04:59.924 --> 00:05:01.994 line:93%
I must become the chairman as if my life depends on it.

00:05:01.994 --> 00:05:03.364 line:93%
I don't have to keep...

00:05:07.635 --> 00:05:09.775 line:93%
those, who stand in my way, alive.

00:05:14.004 --> 00:05:15.044 line:93%
Seo Won.

00:05:19.484 --> 00:05:21.414 line:93%
If I begged you this much,

00:05:23.885 --> 00:05:25.184 line:93%
shouldn't it be enough?

00:05:38.265 --> 00:05:39.405 line:93%
Must I...

00:05:41.934 --> 00:05:43.335 line:93%
beg more than this?

00:06:02.955 --> 00:06:05.095 line:93%
If you eliminated Yoon Seo Won that time,

00:06:05.794 --> 00:06:07.734 line:93%
she wouldn't have been able to cause trouble.

00:06:08.595 --> 00:06:10.664 line:93%
What if that lowlife holds the press conference...

00:06:10.835 --> 00:06:13.004 line:93%
and ruins Boo Cheon? What will you do then?

00:06:17.075 --> 00:06:20.004 line:93%
You only caused our son to injure his leg.

00:06:20.575 --> 00:06:21.814 line:93%
Secretary Oh, do you know that...

00:06:21.975 --> 00:06:24.414 line:93%
you're only harming Boo Cheon?

00:06:36.025 --> 00:06:37.494 line:93%
Kang Pil Joo isn't answering my call.

00:06:38.725 --> 00:06:39.965 line:93%
Bring him to me.

00:07:12.424 --> 00:07:13.564 line:93%
Ms. Na.

00:07:48.434 --> 00:07:49.765 line:93%
It's eventually back...

00:07:51.504 --> 00:07:53.265 line:93%
to the original owner after 20 years.

00:07:55.835 --> 00:07:56.905 line:93%
This is the only thing...

00:07:57.744 --> 00:07:59.674 line:93%
my dad left to me.

00:08:03.645 --> 00:08:04.914 line:93%
Thank you, Ms. Na.

00:08:07.484 --> 00:08:08.585 line:93%
You're welcome,

00:08:09.885 --> 00:08:11.124 line:93%
Mr. Jang Eun Cheon.

00:08:26.604 --> 00:08:28.135 line:93%
Ms. Icheon...

00:08:29.405 --> 00:08:31.075 line:93%
recognized that necklace.

00:08:34.114 --> 00:08:36.915 line:93%
She said Grandfather gave it to Vice Chairman Jang Soo Man.

00:08:42.614 --> 00:08:44.425 line:93%
I thought you were Jo In Ho,

00:08:46.484 --> 00:08:47.854 line:93%
but you were Kang Pil Joo.

00:08:50.925 --> 00:08:52.695 line:93%
Then I thought you were Kang Pil Joo,

00:08:57.264 --> 00:08:59.234 line:93%
but you are Jang Eun Cheon.

00:09:09.874 --> 00:09:11.315 line:93%
Kang Pil Joo's memorial service.

00:09:15.854 --> 00:09:17.884 line:93%
I saw you having a memorial service...

00:09:18.784 --> 00:09:21.455 line:93%
with a name plaque for Kang Pil Joo.

00:09:26.124 --> 00:09:29.234 line:93%
When I saw you having the service with your own name plaque,

00:09:30.465 --> 00:09:31.935 line:93%
I thought about what made you...

00:09:32.734 --> 00:09:34.874 line:93%
walk into the river when you were young.

00:09:37.205 --> 00:09:39.244 line:93%
It must have been something...

00:09:40.675 --> 00:09:43.514 line:93%
terrible and despicable I can't even fathom.

00:09:45.644 --> 00:09:47.455 line:93%
And it's not over yet.

00:09:50.415 --> 00:09:52.124 line:93%
That's what I thought.

00:09:57.624 --> 00:10:00.024 line:93%
I'll take back what I said...

00:10:01.864 --> 00:10:03.134 line:93%
about you living happy.

00:10:06.604 --> 00:10:09.435 line:93%
No matter what you say,

00:10:11.374 --> 00:10:12.945 line:93%
when you can't use your real name,

00:10:14.945 --> 00:10:16.845 line:93%
you're not living well.

00:10:22.514 --> 00:10:23.784 line:93%
I need to know...

00:10:26.055 --> 00:10:29.825 line:93%
me, Boo Cheon, and you...

00:10:32.624 --> 00:10:33.795 line:93%
How three of us...

00:10:35.894 --> 00:10:37.264 line:93%
got here.

00:10:38.165 --> 00:10:39.565 line:93%
And why you are...

00:10:41.634 --> 00:10:43.935 line:93%
hiding your real name...

00:10:45.144 --> 00:10:47.004 line:93%
and living in Cheon A.

00:10:52.884 --> 00:10:54.555 line:93%
I believe I have the right...

00:10:56.854 --> 00:10:58.185 line:93%
to ask you.

00:11:12.104 --> 00:11:13.234 line:93%
I'll tell you,

00:11:17.774 --> 00:11:18.774 line:93%
but...

00:11:21.345 --> 00:11:23.114 line:93%
if you want to hear my story,

00:11:24.545 --> 00:11:27.014 line:93%
you have to be ready for it.

00:11:29.384 --> 00:11:31.254 line:93%
You need to be ready...

00:11:33.725 --> 00:11:35.595 line:93%
to hear...

00:11:36.154 --> 00:11:37.225 line:93%
anything I have to say.

00:11:43.095 --> 00:11:45.665 line:93%
Come back when you're ready.

00:11:47.234 --> 00:11:48.604 line:93%
I am...

00:11:49.975 --> 00:11:51.075 line:93%
ready for it.

00:11:53.675 --> 00:11:54.744 line:93%
So...

00:11:56.675 --> 00:11:57.685 line:93%
tell me.

00:12:07.384 --> 00:12:08.394 line:93%
Attorney Kang.

00:12:16.034 --> 00:12:18.065 line:93%
You need to see Executive Jung now.

00:12:18.364 --> 00:12:20.805 line:93%
She said she called you several times, but you didn't pick up.

00:12:39.925 --> 00:12:41.555 line:93%
Have you found Yoon Seo Won, that witch?

00:12:42.225 --> 00:12:44.864 line:93%
Yes. Boo Cheon's on his way to meet her.

00:12:45.795 --> 00:12:47.634 line:93%
You sent him alone?

00:12:48.764 --> 00:12:51.165 line:93%
He doesn't know anything. What's he going to do?

00:12:51.734 --> 00:12:53.134 line:93%
No one can...

00:12:53.305 --> 00:12:55.835 line:93%
communicate with her better than him.

00:12:56.305 --> 00:12:58.675 line:93%
They even have a child.

00:12:58.874 --> 00:13:02.445 line:93%
I didn't ask how well they get along.

00:13:02.945 --> 00:13:04.644 line:93%
That's not the point.

00:13:04.644 --> 00:13:06.715 line:93%
We need to prevent Yoon Seo Won from talking.

00:13:09.114 --> 00:13:10.114 line:93%
Gosh.

00:13:10.784 --> 00:13:11.784 line:93%
(Boo Cheon)

00:13:14.994 --> 00:13:17.624 line:93%
The number you have dialed isn't available at the moment...

00:13:18.095 --> 00:13:19.165 line:93%
There's...

00:13:19.795 --> 00:13:22.994 line:93%
not one man I like in Mooshimwon.

00:14:50.514 --> 00:14:52.254 line:93%
The number you have dialed...

00:14:52.254 --> 00:14:54.024 line:93%
isn't available at the moment...

00:14:54.425 --> 00:14:57.154 line:93%
He's still not picking up.

00:14:58.095 --> 00:14:59.595 line:93%
Something must've happened.

00:15:19.845 --> 00:15:20.854 line:93%
Mom.

00:15:21.784 --> 00:15:23.415 line:93%
Seo Won will not have...

00:15:24.524 --> 00:15:26.754 line:93%
- a press conference. - Really?

00:15:29.055 --> 00:15:30.654 line:93%
Did you talk her through?

00:15:32.065 --> 00:15:34.095 line:93%
What did you say to change her mind?

00:15:35.494 --> 00:15:37.604 line:93%
I tried my best to beg her.

00:15:38.935 --> 00:15:40.335 line:93%
Then she said she won't do it.

00:15:41.374 --> 00:15:43.305 line:93%
Good job, Boo Cheon.

00:15:44.874 --> 00:15:46.075 line:93%
Of course.

00:15:46.805 --> 00:15:48.144 line:93%
I'll become the chairman.

00:15:48.915 --> 00:15:50.675 line:93%
That's nothing.

00:15:53.244 --> 00:15:56.284 line:93%
We should still lock her up for a while.

00:15:56.354 --> 00:15:59.425 line:93%
Mom. I've settled it.

00:16:01.254 --> 00:16:03.055 line:93%
Trust your son.

00:16:03.354 --> 00:16:04.725 line:93%
Gosh, Mom.

00:16:08.634 --> 00:16:09.634 line:93%
Sure.

00:16:10.734 --> 00:16:12.364 line:93%
I'll trust you...

00:16:13.205 --> 00:16:14.205 line:93%
since you're so certain.

00:16:17.845 --> 00:16:19.244 line:93%
You two should go sleep.

00:16:33.524 --> 00:16:34.524 line:93%
Hey.

00:16:35.925 --> 00:16:36.955 line:93%
That knife...

00:16:40.325 --> 00:16:42.534 line:93%
I needed it to beg Seo Won.

00:16:46.264 --> 00:16:47.774 line:93%
I've put it back to its place.

00:16:48.374 --> 00:16:50.604 line:93%
Don't blame me later if it goes missing.

00:16:53.774 --> 00:16:54.874 line:93%
Let's go to sleep.

00:16:56.244 --> 00:16:57.984 line:93%
You can relax, Mom.

00:17:05.984 --> 00:17:06.984 line:93%
Pil Joo.

00:17:08.054 --> 00:17:09.324 line:93%
Did Boo Cheon just...

00:17:19.435 --> 00:17:21.935 line:93%
(Yoon Seo Won)

00:17:31.784 --> 00:17:33.744 line:93%
Yoon Seo Won's in Cheong A Hotel.

00:17:34.014 --> 00:17:35.254 line:93%
She's not answering her phone.

00:17:35.415 --> 00:17:37.855 line:93%
She must be sleeping. Do you know what time it is?

00:18:02.314 --> 00:18:03.344 line:93%
Yoon Seo Won.

00:18:04.584 --> 00:18:05.685 line:93%
Yoon Seo Won.

00:18:38.115 --> 00:18:41.554 line:93%
(Mooshimwon)

00:18:46.425 --> 00:18:47.554 line:93%
Did it work out?

00:18:50.225 --> 00:18:53.665 line:93%
That's a relief. I knew it.

00:18:53.794 --> 00:18:57.435 line:93%
She was just angry. She didn't really...

00:18:57.905 --> 00:19:00.365 line:93%
You should say hello if you're here.

00:19:24.725 --> 00:19:25.764 line:93%
Here.

00:19:34.034 --> 00:19:36.004 line:93%
I've used it since the day...

00:19:36.004 --> 00:19:38.605 line:93%
I started Cheong A business.

00:19:39.105 --> 00:19:40.105 line:93%
Grandfather.

00:19:40.945 --> 00:19:43.244 line:93%
I told him that you'd prefer...

00:19:43.244 --> 00:19:46.244 line:93%
receiving the shares or cash.

00:19:46.344 --> 00:19:49.715 line:93%
But he wanted to give it to you,

00:19:49.715 --> 00:19:52.355 line:93%
so he took it out a few days ago.

00:19:52.625 --> 00:19:55.324 line:93%
He even asked me to apply the lubricant on it...

00:19:55.895 --> 00:19:57.925 line:93%
and treat it as if it were a baby...

00:19:57.925 --> 00:19:59.425 line:93%
so that its beads won't fall off.

00:19:59.425 --> 00:20:02.465 line:93%
He was such a demanding man.

00:20:02.695 --> 00:20:04.734 line:93%
Are you disappointed that it's not the shares?

00:20:06.135 --> 00:20:07.304 line:93%
I am not, Grandfather.

00:20:08.135 --> 00:20:09.574 line:93%
I like it better than the shares.

00:20:10.844 --> 00:20:13.244 line:93%
Of course, I would've been happier if you gave me the shares too.

00:20:13.244 --> 00:20:17.314 line:93%
Look, this little boy now has grown into a decent man.

00:20:17.685 --> 00:20:19.915 line:93%
You're much better than your dad.

00:20:21.254 --> 00:20:24.425 line:93%
Sir, there's one more thing you should tell him.

00:20:24.584 --> 00:20:26.324 line:93%
- What? - You used the abacus...

00:20:26.324 --> 00:20:28.925 line:93%
in front of the customers...

00:20:28.925 --> 00:20:30.524 line:93%
just not to incur their suspicion.

00:20:30.625 --> 00:20:32.665 line:93%
But you were already done...

00:20:32.665 --> 00:20:35.264 line:93%
calculating the prices in your head.

00:20:35.635 --> 00:20:36.895 line:93%
That's right.

00:20:36.895 --> 00:20:40.564 line:93%
I could do sums in my head faster than using it.

00:20:41.274 --> 00:20:42.605 line:93%
You're still the one...

00:20:42.605 --> 00:20:44.744 line:93%
who reads Cheong A's financial statements the fastest.

00:20:44.744 --> 00:20:46.774 line:93%
That's the vital aspect required for businessmen.

00:20:47.175 --> 00:20:50.514 line:93%
You need to know what would bring you the most profit quickly...

00:20:50.544 --> 00:20:53.185 line:93%
and then pretend not to know anything...

00:20:53.215 --> 00:20:54.355 line:93%
with a poker face.

00:20:54.355 --> 00:20:55.784 line:93%
With a poker face!

00:20:57.455 --> 00:20:58.554 line:93%
I got it.

00:20:59.425 --> 00:21:00.554 line:93%
I'll keep that it mind.

00:21:00.554 --> 00:21:03.455 line:93%
I opened Cheong A business when I was 19,

00:21:03.455 --> 00:21:05.824 line:93%
so I guess the abacus is about 60 years old, right?

00:21:05.824 --> 00:21:07.395 line:93%
It'd be around 70 years old.

00:21:07.395 --> 00:21:08.764 line:93%
Really?

00:21:08.935 --> 00:21:11.334 line:93%
I guess I want to rejuvenate myself...

00:21:11.334 --> 00:21:13.205 line:93%
since I often believe I'm younger than I really am.

00:21:17.975 --> 00:21:19.105 line:93%
Then Ha Jung will...

00:21:20.145 --> 00:21:23.074 line:93%
lose his chance to become the member of the Jang family.

00:21:24.385 --> 00:21:26.215 line:93%
Boo Cheon begged me.

00:21:34.794 --> 00:21:37.324 line:93%
Call off Yoon Seo Won's press conference.

00:21:37.564 --> 00:21:38.594 line:93%
Yes, sir.

00:21:54.814 --> 00:21:57.544 line:93%
I didn't even know about its existence.

00:21:57.544 --> 00:21:58.615 line:93%
Grandfather...

00:21:59.014 --> 00:22:02.185 line:93%
only showed it to Dad just once and kept it until today.

00:22:02.554 --> 00:22:03.984 line:93%
And he gave it to me.

00:22:05.885 --> 00:22:09.094 line:93%
Attorney Kang and Director Jang have just got out of the hospital.

00:22:09.455 --> 00:22:11.195 line:93%
What would invigorate them?

00:22:11.195 --> 00:22:13.965 line:93%
What about Master Kwon's herbal tonic?

00:22:17.435 --> 00:22:20.304 line:93%
Ms. Na should have some more.

00:22:21.034 --> 00:22:22.074 line:93%
I'm all right.

00:22:22.574 --> 00:22:24.605 line:93%
Mother, I don't need it.

00:22:24.605 --> 00:22:26.945 line:93%
You need it, so you can conceive a baby.

00:22:26.945 --> 00:22:28.215 line:93%
Director Jang even gave...

00:22:28.415 --> 00:22:31.344 line:93%
Ms. Na the family treasure.

00:22:32.244 --> 00:22:34.855 line:93%
Why don't you make Honorary Chairman Jan happy...

00:22:34.855 --> 00:22:36.185 line:93%
by giving birth to a baby boy?

00:22:36.814 --> 00:22:37.925 line:93%
Family treasure?

00:22:38.054 --> 00:22:41.494 line:93%
I mean the necklace that the late vice chairman Jang had.

00:22:46.094 --> 00:22:49.395 line:93%
The necklace Honorary Chairman made himself...

00:22:49.534 --> 00:22:51.804 line:93%
after winning some kind of bid for construction...

00:22:51.804 --> 00:22:55.274 line:93%
when the vice chairman was little.

00:22:58.544 --> 00:23:00.074 line:93%
I have never seen it.

00:23:01.945 --> 00:23:05.314 line:93%
Then I'm sure Honorary Chairman Jang gave it to you.

00:23:05.314 --> 00:23:07.385 line:93%
I just found it somewhere else.

00:23:07.784 --> 00:23:08.855 line:93%
Really?

00:23:10.215 --> 00:23:11.984 line:93%
But it looked the same.

00:23:11.984 --> 00:23:13.225 line:93%
I know what it looks like.

00:23:14.254 --> 00:23:16.594 line:93%
Bring it here. I need to see it.

00:23:17.695 --> 00:23:18.764 line:93%
Yes, Mother.

00:23:38.115 --> 00:23:40.885 line:93%
It's inside the bottom drawer left to the desk.

00:24:08.814 --> 00:24:12.084 line:93%
I found the place for Seo Won and Ha Jung to stay.

00:24:12.445 --> 00:24:15.814 line:93%
We need to estrange them from Boo Cheon for a while.

00:24:15.915 --> 00:24:18.984 line:93%
Finally, you have control over Yoon Seo Won.

00:24:23.094 --> 00:24:25.665 line:93%
Why do you always cover up for her?

00:24:26.965 --> 00:24:29.064 line:93%
There's no reason for it, Executive Jung.

00:24:29.334 --> 00:24:30.494 line:93%
You never do anything...

00:24:31.264 --> 00:24:33.135 line:93%
without a reason.

00:24:34.605 --> 00:24:36.334 line:93%
I guess that means you can't tell me why.

00:24:37.905 --> 00:24:40.975 line:93%
Fine. I will stop asking why.

00:24:42.774 --> 00:24:46.544 line:93%
Boo Cheon could've changed so much thanks to your encouragement,

00:24:46.744 --> 00:24:47.984 line:93%
which is really good.

00:24:48.554 --> 00:24:51.855 line:93%
Both Boo Cheon and I think this would be the last chance.

00:24:52.725 --> 00:24:56.024 line:93%
Cheong A is currently under attack from others.

00:24:56.324 --> 00:24:59.195 line:93%
He thinks there would be no such chance later,

00:24:59.294 --> 00:25:01.465 line:93%
so he's been nervous a lot,

00:25:02.135 --> 00:25:05.405 line:93%
which I believe to be helpful for Boo Cheon.

00:25:06.834 --> 00:25:08.135 line:93%
I see.

00:25:44.344 --> 00:25:47.205 line:93%
Where did you find it?

00:25:47.445 --> 00:25:48.544 line:93%
I went to a retreat...

00:25:48.844 --> 00:25:51.145 line:93%
and found it near the river when I was young.

00:25:51.645 --> 00:25:53.844 line:93%
Where? Which river?

00:25:54.314 --> 00:25:56.855 line:93%
It was near the retreat center in Gapyeong.

00:26:02.824 --> 00:26:03.955 line:93%
Leave it here.

00:26:08.395 --> 00:26:09.895 line:93%
It's not yours.

00:26:10.665 --> 00:26:12.465 line:93%
Do you cherish it now?

00:26:19.504 --> 00:26:22.074 line:93%
This belong to the Jangs,

00:26:23.044 --> 00:26:24.544 line:93%
specifically to my husband.

00:26:25.344 --> 00:26:26.514 line:93%
Let me make it clear...

