and noble task.

00:49:41.014 --> 00:49:42.214 line:93%
Of course, you're tired.

00:49:42.415 --> 00:49:43.545 line:93%
It's noble.

00:49:43.545 --> 00:49:46.315 line:93%
I always keep what you said in mind,

00:49:46.384 --> 00:49:47.614 line:93%
and when there are guests,

00:49:47.685 --> 00:49:51.284 line:93%
I serve them as if they're...

00:49:51.485 --> 00:49:53.154 line:93%
my late parents.

