I'm here to apologize.

00:51:22.514 --> 00:51:23.514 line:93%
Father.

00:51:24.614 --> 00:51:25.714 line:93%
I...

00:51:26.384 --> 00:51:28.955 line:93%
will back off,

00:51:30.685 --> 00:51:33.054 line:93%
but please forgive Yeo Cheon.

00:51:35.554 --> 00:51:39.194 line:93%
This won't solve anything.

00:51:39.725 --> 00:51:42.665 line:93%
Attorney Kang. Why don't you stay mutual...

00:51:43.134 --> 00:51:45.005 line:93%
and suggest a plan for Cheong A?

00:51:45.705 --> 00:51:49.735 line:93%
It's cost a lot of money and time...

00:51:50.005 --> 00:51:52.145 line:93%
to prevent the public from knowing...

00:51:52.645 --> 00:51:55.074 line:93%
what Director Jang Yeo Cheon has done wrong.

00:51:56.145 --> 00:51:59.344 line:93%
Many people say his relegation...

00:51:59.915 --> 00:52:02.784 line:93%
has set a good example to management.

00:52:03.455 --> 00:52:04.554 line:93%
If...

00:52:04.924 --> 00:52:07.694 line:93%
his relegation is canceled,

00:52:08.554 --> 00:52:10.594 line:93%
I believe it is an action against...

00:52:10.725 --> 00:52:12.594 line:93%
Honorary Chairman's belief...

00:52:12.964 --> 00:52:15.194 line:93%
of making anyone who harms Cheong A...

