take responsibility.

00:52:22.074 --> 00:52:24.444 line:93%
- Yeo Cheon. - Yes, Grandfather.

00:52:24.705 --> 00:52:27.145 line:93%
It's against my belief.

00:52:27.475 --> 00:52:28.744 line:93%
I can't take it back.

00:52:29.875 --> 00:52:31.485 line:93%
Go work at the lumber camp.

00:52:45.964 --> 00:52:46.964 line:93%
How did...

