- Hello? - Boo Cheon.

00:53:25.705 --> 00:53:28.134 line:93%
- I'm sorry, - About what?

00:53:28.804 --> 00:53:31.875 line:93%
but I'm going to tell Ms. Na...

00:53:33.045 --> 00:53:35.344 line:93%
that your marriage was my idea.

00:53:36.614 --> 00:53:37.744 line:93%
I thought...

00:53:38.145 --> 00:53:40.714 line:93%
I should tell you...

00:53:41.755 --> 00:53:43.585 line:93%
- before I tell her. - what?

00:53:44.585 --> 00:53:46.085 line:93%
Are you out of your mind?

00:53:47.494 --> 00:53:48.594 line:93%
Don't do that.

00:53:49.295 --> 00:53:50.295 line:93%
Hey...

00:53:52.694 --> 00:53:54.534 line:93%
What a jerk.

00:54:07.844 --> 00:54:10.214 line:93%
- Hello, Director Kang. - Long time no see.

00:54:12.045 --> 00:54:13.685 line:93%
Where's Executive Na?

00:54:13.685 --> 00:54:16.255 line:93%
She went out for lunch at the restaurant in front of the building.

00:54:18.525 --> 00:54:21.054 line:93%
(Bonjuk and Bibimbap Cafe)

00:54:27.094 --> 00:54:28.094 line:93%
Ms. Na.

00:54:29.594 --> 00:54:30.735 line:93%
Mr. Kang.

00:54:32.005 --> 00:54:33.464 line:93%
What are you doing here?

00:54:33.964 --> 00:54:35.074 line:93%
Can I sit down?

00:54:36.005 --> 00:54:37.034 line:93%
Yes.

