Did you know...

00:59:30.065 --> 00:59:31.835 line:93%
people call me...

00:59:36.904 --> 00:59:37.944 line:93%
Cheong A's dog?

00:59:42.415 --> 00:59:44.185 line:93%
My goal for Cheong A...

00:59:45.514 --> 00:59:46.645 line:93%
is to make...

00:59:48.114 --> 00:59:49.315 line:93%
my owner,

00:59:50.214 --> 00:59:52.154 line:93%
Jang Boo Cheon, the chairman.

