01:00:08.335 --> 01:00:11.804 line:93%
to earn the approval for Cheong A Tower construction.

01:00:12.005 --> 01:00:13.475 line:93%
So I thought...

01:00:14.145 --> 01:00:16.344 line:93%
the daughter of Congressman Na Gi Chul,

01:00:18.085 --> 01:00:19.114 line:93%
the presidential candidate,

01:00:19.944 --> 01:00:22.485 line:93%
would be perfect...

01:00:23.685 --> 01:00:24.924 line:93%
as Boo Cheon's match.

