01:04:30.904 --> 01:04:32.464 line:93%
for strength,

01:04:35.435 --> 01:04:37.335 line:93%
so I could save this boy.

01:04:39.875 --> 01:04:41.514 line:93%
I prayed...

01:04:43.344 --> 01:04:44.384 line:93%
and prayed...

01:04:45.844 --> 01:04:47.344 line:93%
until you woke up.

